Wow, that's impressive.

45
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:29,940
Yes.

46
00:02:29,940 --> 00:02:31,640
Well, they have to be able
to handle whatever comes

47
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:33,010
Their way, right
Detective Carter?

48
00:02:33,010 --> 00:02:33,950
Yeah.

49
