Detective Carter,
this is Annie Grayson.

51
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:40,590
She's going to be
working with us.

52
00:02:40,590 --> 00:02:41,290
Welcome aboard.

53
00:02:41,290 --> 00:02:41,990
Thank you.

54
