Hello?

57
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:52,560
My name is Grace.

58
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:55,320
Can't tell you tell me yours?

59
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:57,650
Can you tell me your name?

60
00:02:57,650 --> 00:02:59,120
Jacob.

61
00:02:59,120 --> 00:02:59,820
Jacob.

62
00:02:59,820 --> 00:03:01,790
Do you need some help, Jacob?

63
00:03:01,790 --> 00:03:02,490
Jacob.

64
00:03:02,490 --> 00:03:03,690
Please don't hide
from your father.

65
00:03:03,690 --> 00:03:04,450
Don't hang up.

66
