Call us back.

74
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:25,060
You know I have things to do.

75
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:25,750
Where are you?

76
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:27,230
[PHONE RINGING]

77
00:03:27,230 --> 00:03:28,480
Childhelp.

78
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,410
National Abuse Hotline.

79
00:03:30,410 --> 00:03:32,730
Jacob?

80
00:03:32,730 --> 00:03:34,220
Keep talking.

81
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:35,570
Just keep the line on.

82
00:03:35,570 --> 00:03:36,620
Jacob, is that you again?

83
